Setup of Angular:
		1: Install Nodejs using the following command
			apt-get install nodejs
	
		2: Install the angular CLI using the following command
			npm install -g  @angular/cli
			
Startup Angular:

	Creating Project:
		
		1: Create project using the following command
				ng new angularProjectName

		2: Install bootstrap framework on your project using this command in your project 		     directory
				npm install bootstrap –save
		
			Now, add the following code inside the angular.json file
				“Styles”:[
					“src/style.css”,
					“./node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css”		
					],	
	Bulding and Executing:
			
		1: To Bulid the project
			ng serve

		2: To Build the project and start the server
			ng serve -o

